@Node "Introd"

@{b}ECFAX Enhancer@{ub} is a GUI based interface based on ElChipoFax, writen with
SAS C 5.10 and GADTOOLSBOX V2.0.

@{b}ECFAX Enhancer @{ub} is SHAREWARE, you can distribute by the way you like but
you must respect these principles :


        You must distribute @{b}ECFAX Enhancer@{ub} in his integrity.

