@{b}@{u}ECFAX Enhancer.features@{ub}@{uu}

        - C= Installer for easy installation.
        - 850 lines of AmigaGuide format doc.
        - ASCII pages preparing to Group 3 fax format.
        - Font choice for ASCII/G3 convertion (include CGFONTS).
        - IFF pages preparing to group 3 fax format.
        - Fax sending by the way of every CLASS 2 compatible modems.
        - Group 3 faxs files to iff files convertion.
        - El Chipo Fax features remain accessible in CLI mode.
        - GUI Interface is strictly C= Guide line compatible.
        - Only one Intuition way for El chipo Fax command access.
        - Faxsend log file.
        - Black and white convertion inverting.
        - Invert sending Bit order.
        - Auto three lines + Date and time header with every fax send.
        - choice betwen several rewritable header files.
        - 50 numbers rewritable Phone book with comments.
        - Icone mode (for minor 680xx time use).
        - défault parameters ToolTypes seting.
        - automatique type file convert detection (asc or iff)
        - faxs idle task reception.
        - Auto record of cfg seting in toolstypes.

