@Node "compa"

        @{b}COMPATIBILITY@{ub}

        ECFAX EH need at least 512kb of ram and 39.106 kickstart.
        (I think kick 37.175 can also be suported).

        Programm and data can be installed on flopy or Hard disk.

        Copy, Assign and delete command must be in C: drawer.

        ECFAXEH is compatible with all fax modem type CLASS 2.



