@Node "Nouv"

 07/11/93       - version 1.0 , All is new !.

 12/11/93       - version 1.0.1
                  ink/paper can now be inverted.

 13/11/93       - version 1.0.2
                  Fax Send can now write a log file when sending.

                - Bug in installer which give Service: as final destination
                  at every time is now corected.

                - From version 1.0.2 El Chipo Fax original doc is provided
                  with the package.

 15/11/93       - version 1.0.3
                  IFFTOFAX and ASCTOFAX commands now works wityh '-r' option
                  for Concaten possibility.

                - Header lines are now added.

 18/11/93       - version 1.0.3b
                  Depth gadgets added.

                  Bug which stop recepting fax when header lines was more
                  than 80 char long ,in precedent version is now corrected.
                  Headers line can be send correctly now.
                  A Delay loop has been added in IDCMP handle to preserve
                  680x0 time.

 21/11/93       - version 1.0.4
                  A busy indicator show the state of programm.
                  You can now make a choice of Fonts and size for ascii
                  to fax conversion (including CG Fonts).


 04/12/93       - version 1.0.5
                  Recessed gadget has been added to reduce size of ECFAXEH
                  window when is not in use.

                  Dest can now be chosen in a 50 numbers and comments list.
                  All numbers and comments are modifiable.
                  Install now permit installing ECFAXEH with v36 of
                  kickstart.

 17/12/93       - version 1.0.6
                  IFF TO FAX and ASC TO FAX gadgets are now repaced by a
                  single CONVERT gadget, the command is able to detect type
                  of file to convert (ASCII or IFF).
                  All of parameters can be set by TOOLTYPES options.
                  BO_Send and BO_Conv options are added, they permit to
                  invert bit send order for using ECFAXEH with Supra
                  fax/modem.
                  Recessed bar is now replaced by an APPICONE on workbench
                  screen, Recess gadget is replaced by Icone gadget.
                  Header def window now display last header definitions
                  when open.
                  It's now possible to define more than one Header file.
                  Appicones and files Icones are now created by GetDiskObject
                  and PutDiskObject commands more compatible with furtur
                  version of KS.

 01/01/1994       - version 1.0.7
                  From this version, ECFAXEH become SHAREWARE.
                  Unregistered version display a register window when open.
                  It's the only limitation of unregistered version.
                  CFG gadget is added to record configuration in ToolTypes.
                  Recv gadget is added, it's a major enhancement, from this
                  version ECFAXEH can receive fax.
                  Wait signal is added to know the state if programm is in
                  receive mode.
                  ECFAXEH Appicone have now tow image, one for programm in
                  normal mode, and other for programm in receive mode.
                  FAXRECV toolTypes is added launch the programm in receive
                  mode.

